{"fsPath":"/home/khanh/src/0_github/Tardis-1/workflows/session_init.md","fileUuid":"a1f01b2d-3c0f-4781-b471-df72302c7e89","fileSizeBytes":1641,"numLines":52,"diffChanges":[{"originalStartLineNumberOneIndexed":1,"originalEndLineNumberExclusiveOneIndexed":1,"modifiedStartLineNumberOneIndexed":1,"modifiedEndLineNumberExclusiveOneIndexed":53,"addedLines":["# session_init","","## Objective","","Start a learning session by selecting the next concept node from scheduler output and generating an adversarial prompt aligned to the weakest eligible node.","","## Required Inputs","","- SQLite database path (default: `.tmp/tardis.db`)","- Session ID (string)","- Optional category filter","","## Tools","","- `tools/scheduler.py` - rank next concept candidates.","- `tools/adversarial_generator.py` - generate deterministic adversarial scenarios from weak nodes.","","## Steps","","1. Ensure the database exists. If not, run:","   - `python tools/init_db.py`","   - `python tools/seed_concepts.py`","2. Select the next concept:","   - `python tools/scheduler.py --output .tmp/session_next.json --limit 1`","3. Generate adversarial scenarios:","   - `python tools/adversarial_generator.py --output .tmp/session_scenarios.json --top-k 3`","4. Match the top scheduler node with the corresponding generated scenario by `node_id`.","5. Emit the session start payload to `.tmp/session_init_<session_id>.json` with:","   - `session_id`","   - `node_id`","   - `concept_name`","   - `scenario_variant`","   - `prompt`","","## Output","","- Final destination: `.tmp/session_init_<session_id>.json`","- Intermediate files:","  - `.tmp/session_next.json`","  - `.tmp/session_scenarios.json`","","## Edge Cases and Recovery","","- Empty scheduler candidates:","  - Re-run scheduler with a lower prerequisite floor in `config/misconception_thresholds.json`.","- Scenario not found for selected `node_id`:","  - Regenerate with higher `--top-k` and verify seed data.","","## Learning Notes","","- If a node is repeatedly selected but unresolved, reduce scheduler weight on due time and increase mastery-gap weight.",""],"tokenizedAddedLines":[1000000,1000001,1000002,1000001,1000003,1000001,1000004,1000001,1000005,1000006,1000007,1000001,1000008,1000001,1000009,1000010,1000001,1000011,1000001,1000012,1000013,1000014,1000015,1000016,1000017,1000018,1000019,1000020,1000021,1000022,1000023,1000024,1000025,1000001,1000026,1000001,1000027,1000028,1000029,1000030,1000001,1000031,1000001,1000032,1000033,1000034,1000035,1000001,1000036,1000001,1000037,1000001]}],"gitInfo":{"gitInfo":{"gitRoot":"/home/khanh/src/0_github/Tardis-1","branch":"main","commitHash":"fcbc4c272962a55f6dbf1e27d263242d5a96971f"}},"kind":"KIND_ADDED"}